.SH VORTO(1) A-vorto User Manual
.SS NAME
.PP
vorto - personal wordbook microapp
.SS SYNOPSIS
.PP
\f[B]A vorto\f[R] [\f[I]command\f[R]] [\f[I]options\f[R]]
[\f[I]arguments\f[R]]
.SS DESCRIPTION
.PP
A-vorto is a personal wordbook (vortaro) microapp for storing and
managing vocabulary with definitions, usage examples, categories, and
cross-references.
.SS COMMANDS
.SS list
.TP
List all word entries.
\f[V]A vorto list [-o FIELD] [-d] [-l LIMIT]\f[R]
.SS vidi
.TP
View a word entry.
\f[V]A vorto vidi UUID [--html] [--ref]\f[R]
.SS aldoni
.TP
Add a new word entry.
\f[V]A vorto aldoni TEXT [OPTIONS]\f[R]
.SS modifi
.TP
Modify a word entry.
\f[V]A vorto modifi UUID [OPTIONS]\f[R]
.SS forigi
.TP
Delete a word entry.
\f[V]A vorto forigi UUID [--hard]\f[R]
.SS serchi
.TP
Full-text search.
\f[V]A vorto serchi QUERY [--fuzzy] [-l LIMIT]\f[R]
.SS malfari
.TP
Undo the last operation.
\f[V]A vorto malfari\f[R]
.SS rubujo
.TP
List entries in trash.
\f[V]A vorto rubujo [-l LIMIT]\f[R]
.SS restaurigi
.TP
Restore an entry from trash.
\f[V]A vorto restaurigi UUID\f[R]
.SS senrubujigi
.TP
Empty trash.
\f[V]A vorto senrubujigi [-d DAYS]\f[R]
.SS importi
.TP
Import from JSON file.
\f[V]A vorto importi PATH [--password PASSWORD]\f[R]
.SS eksporti
.TP
Export to JSON/TOML file.
\f[V]A vorto eksporti PATH [-f FORMAT] [--password PASSWORD]\f[R]
